## Project Evolution (V7 → V11.20)

Since V7, Cat AI has evolved from a simple AI-powered cat stool classification application into a comprehensive intelligent cat health management platform.

### V7
- AI-based stool image classification
- Health prediction using a deep learning model
- Basic web interface
- Health history recording

### V8
- Improved user interface and workflow
- Enhanced visualization of prediction results
- Better history management
- More stable image upload and processing

### V9
- Introduced cat profile management
- Support for cat photo uploads
- AI-generated dietary recommendations
- Personalized health suggestions
- Improved data organization

### V10
- Multi-user account system
- User registration and authentication
- SQLite database integration
- User profile management
- Avatar uploads
- Emergency contact information
- API configuration support

### V11
- Multi-cat management
- AI litter box monitoring
- Entry and exit detection with AI feedback
- Gemini-powered AI assistant
- Health report generation
- Improved history filtering and management
- Modernized user interface
- Enhanced performance and stability

### V11.20
The latest release focuses on reliability and user experience.

Major improvements include:
- Rebuilt global location management system
- Local-first region database architecture
- Chinese localization for countries and regions
- Three-level country, state/province, and city selector
- Background database updates
- Offline fallback support
- Faster page loading
- Better timeout and error handling
- Manual city input when region data is unavailable

---

## Overall Progress

Cat AI has grown from a simple image classification prototype into a full-stack AI-powered pet healthcare platform featuring:

- AI health analysis
- Multi-user authentication
- Multi-cat profile management
- Smart litter box monitoring
- AI dietary recommendations
- Health history tracking
- PDF health reports
- Personalized user profiles
- Global localization support
- Modern web application architecture
- Continuous performance and reliability improvements
